data.description: Welcome to Woodlawn! This spacious 2nd floor condo features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathroom, & 1 one parking space in a gated parking lot in the rear of the building. This unit has hardwood flooring throughout, living room with fireplace & enclosed sun room, dining room, kitchen with breakfast bar peninsula, granite counters, cabinetry with white appliance package: dishwasher, refrigerator, & range. Enjoy the outdoors on your private balcony off the kitchen & private deck in the rear of the building. In-unit washer/dryer. En suite with private bathroom, walk-in closet, & hardwood flooring. 2nd & 3rd bedrooms have hardwood flooring. Other features include ceiling fans with lighting in the main living area & all bedrooms. Doors close to public transportation, University of Chicago, & in close proximity to the home of the Obama Presidential Center.
